  "schema:name": "Processed ship-based Multibeam Sonar Data (version 2) acquired in the Pacific Ocean during the Thomas Washington expedition PASC03WT (1983)",
  "schema:citation": "GMRT, (2012), Processed ship-based Multibeam Sonar Data (version 2) acquired in the Pacific Ocean during the Thomas Washington expedition PASC03WT (1983). Interdisciplinary Earth Data Alliance (IEDA). doi:10.26022/IEDA/316815",
